# {{appName}} - Apache Cordova App

This is an Apache Cordova project for building Android apps with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Project Structure

```
app/
├── www/           # Your web assets (HTML, CSS, JS)
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── css/
│   └── js/
├── platforms/     # Platform-specific code (auto-generated)
├── plugins/       # Cordova plugins
└── config.xml     # Cordova configuration
```

## Getting Started

1. Edit your web files in `app/www/`
2. Use the **Web Preview** to test in browser
3. Use the **Android Preview** to test on the emulator

## Common Commands

```bash
cd app

# Add a plugin
cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-camera

# Build for Android
cordova build android

# Run on Android emulator
cordova run android

# Run in browser
cordova run browser
```

